The Glenn Beck Program

The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 2/21/14Friday, February 21, 2014 11:02 AM

As video surfaces of NFL Running Back Ray Rice,
   dragging his unconscious girlfriend out of an elevator,
     Glenn wants to know why the NFL allows thugs in the league.

  Also, the latest out of the chaos and violence in the Ukraine,
       and Glenn's fear that Russia will put troops on the ground.

  Plus, how the government is targeting news rooms 
       and the internet and how Americans can't let this happen!
